:0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"Why<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709e5f90e899b14eaec81ca33b4620a2e4a0f8f9","tid":1816491,"uid":17904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T14:21:28.000Z","msg":"10日太趕"},{"pid":"0c2b9fed697ebe9068576260c116652684b2bfb6","tid":1816491,"uid":265932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"224c9821de6f939ae7ef8ed12482e211495ead86","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"小弟打算4月頭同個fd去行abc<br />\n行程大約10日(連埋飛)<br />\n實質可能行8-9日左右<br />\n想問有冇可能行埋poon hill?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOr淨係行abc算？好似唔洗咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs:2個都有做下運動既 嚟緊都準備train下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋想問下如果去到當地先搞簽證會唔會搞好耐?<br />\n麻煩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T22:27:24.000Z","msg":"我7月雨季去abc，不過之後冇錢去埋poon hill, 俾你參巧我嘅日數<br />\n<br />\n6月26中午落地<span style=\"color: red;\">加德滿都</span><br />\n6月27夜晚到<span style=\"color: green;\">Pokhara</span><br />\n<br />\n6月28中午喺<span style=\"color: blue;\">Phedi</span>上山<br />\n當日夜晚8點到<span style=\"color: purple;\">Tolka</span>(1800m)落腳<br />\n<br />\n6月29日夜晚6點到<span style=\"color: violet;\">Chhomrong</span> <br />\n6月30下午4點到<span style=\"color: pink;\">Dovan</span><br />\n7月1下午4點到<span style=\"color: gold;\">魚尾峰大本營</span><br />\n<br />\n7月2凌晨6點成功登頂<br />\n當日朝早8點全速落山<br />\n夜晚6點落山去到2000米<span style=\"color: violet;\">chhomrong</span> 附近<br />\n<br />\n7月3 繼續落山，到中午同一個新疆人夾錢坐Jeep落山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 1000尼泊爾盧比一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果之後去埋poon hill嘅話就要喺落山第二日，經過<span style=\"color: violet;\">Chhomrong</span>(2177m)嘅時轉向西走，由2177上到Poon Hill(3210m), 要幾耐自己大概可以計到。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果你有錢而想走捷徑可以喺Pokhara搵jeep車你上山先開始，可以省返幾個鐘，唔一定跟我喺<span style=\"color: blue;\">Phedi</span>入口開始。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TgxXSmp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTgxXSmp.jpg&h=abfd2d1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bad06e6769daa74c79bd2415b8d25ffb9d8a9ceb","tid":1816491,"uid":296005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"224c9821de6f939ae7ef8ed12482e211495ead86","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"小弟打算4月頭同個fd去行abc<br />\n行程大約10日(連埋飛)<br />\n實質可能行8-9日左右<br />\n想問有冇可能行埋poon hill?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOr淨係行abc算？好似唔洗咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs:2個都有做下運動既 嚟緊都準備train下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋想問下如果去到當地先搞簽證會唔會搞好耐?<br />\n麻煩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"落地簽證，要等半曰<br />\n因為佢要揸車去整<br />\n<br />\n我上次都係around 4月去<br />\npoon hill 係值得去，abc 連poon hill 7 day係夠既<br />\n5 day 的話，你要行得幾快<br />\n<br />\nBTW日落後唔好沖涼"},{"pid":"999d39087af015cc92df2b2753ff951602df9057","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c2b9fed697ebe9068576260c116652684b2bfb6","tid":1816491,"uid":265932,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"224c9821de6f939ae7ef8ed12482e211495ead86","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"小弟打算4月頭同個fd去行abc<br />\n行程大約10日(連埋飛)<br />\n實質可能行8-9日左右<br />\n想問有冇可能行埋poon hill?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOr淨係行abc算？好似唔洗咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs:2個都有做下運動既 嚟緊都準備train下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋想問下如果去到當地先搞簽證會唔會搞好耐?<br />\n麻煩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gi