.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"一路行有民居會有guest house 大把野食同地方瞓<br />\n我果陣行一日基本上剩係食dal bhat <br />\n因為可以無限添飯同餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太凍加杯熱飲<br />\n低海拔大約1500-2200盧比一日<br />\n高海拔 2000-3000盧比一日 <br />\n<br />\n以上包左每日裝水 房錢 早午晚三餐<br />\n咩guide porter都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:25:10.000Z","msg":"無porter都上到 咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"有兩碌行山杖 孭大約10-15kg<br />\n平時有運動開練開肌耐力<br />\n好多人都行到上去㗎<br />\n唔洗咁擔心<br />\n<br />\n我平時都冇行開山 <br />\n都係打下拳做gym"},{"pid":"f40a417bbb1cef42cae1fce2e6c0511729476e86","tid":1816491,"uid":243516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad4349ac5d2d96dbd183c653799ca1cc22dfe8e7","tid":1816491,"uid":91966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f253e1d651658b3e60b2f28a1fe44f4697744164","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad06e6769daa74c79bd2415b8d25ffb9d8a9ceb","tid":1816491,"uid":296005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"落地簽證，要等半曰<br />\n因為佢要揸車去整<br />\n<br />\n我上次都係around 4月去<br />\npoon hill 係值得去，abc 連poon hill 7 day係夠既<br />\n5 day 的話，你要行得幾快<br />\n<br />\nBTW日落後唔好沖涼"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T01:59:10.000Z","msg":"同埋想問下點解日落後唔好沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:16:32.000Z","msg":"沖唔沖涼要睇溫度同高度而定<br />\n因為上到太高海拔太凍沖涼有可能會冷親然後感冒<br />\n係高海拔傷風感冒係好高風險既事嚟<br />\n而尼泊爾溫差大所以日落後唔好沖涼<br />\n費事冷親啦<br />\n<br />\n我諗夏天3500米以下日落前沖涼都係冇咩問題<br />\n不過冬天就不了<br />\n搵條手巾仔洗下碌鳩洗下面求其抹下就算數啦<br />\n我果陣夏天行因為慳錢要比錢沖熱水涼既話就唔會沖<br />\n<br />\n所以7日有5日係冇沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最尾果日浸溫泉簡直爽到想即場打翻個飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:49:45.000Z","msg":"我記得戈陣時去嘅時候佢地嘅熱水都係話靠太陽能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要沖熱水涼都最好快啲沖<br />\n愈夜愈大機會會無熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45d06abbbd4c2c318397f603f9edbb5863383526","tid":1816491,"uid":243516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"371f578acfdde9b73435a792eebaf0ed99ed9887","tid":1816491,"uid":91966,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d467aa450c67e5db7f138c5a4139c9bd6c1d90df","tid":1816491,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44e558440da11a08ce2eef5e71539fd32acd660a","tid":1816491,"uid":91966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"一路行有民居會有guest house 大把野食同地方瞓<br />\n我果陣行一日基本上剩係食dal bhat <br />\n因為可以無限添飯同餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n太凍加杯熱飲<br />\n低海拔大約1500-2200盧比一日<br />\n高海拔 2000-3000盧比一日 <br />\n<br />\n以上包左每日裝水 房錢 早午晚三餐<br />\n咩guide porter都冇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:25:10.000Z","msg":"無porter都上到 咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:33:22.000Z","msg":"有兩碌行山杖 孭大約10-15kg<br />\n平時有運動開練開肌耐力<br />\n好多人都行到上去㗎<br />\n唔洗咁擔心<br />\n<br />\n我平時都冇行開山 <br />\n都係打下拳做gym"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T19:51:16.000Z","msg":"正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾年前一月去嘅時候都好多人<br />\n而且沿途路標都好清楚 差唔多係得一條路徑<br />\n所以唔駛咁擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"415241bb0c95fef0585a9b5684dda3e6b9a6f072","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T21:18:39.000Z","msg":"我果陣時自己一個行abc+poon hill<br />\n冇guide冇porter<br />\n由naya pul開始行<br />\npoon hill<br />\nannapurna base camp<br />\n順時針一圈回到naya pul<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔易行 雖然d人話係家樂徑<br />\n3月尾開始有雨，但3000米以上有雪<br />\n高山反應同山上感冒好大件事"},{"pid":"70a8889f7769146bbf7edbecdef519dcdcedb419","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T22:02:41.000Z","msg":"你可以下載一個行山app叫<br />\n<a href=\"http://maps.me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmaps.me&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=a684a8fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">maps.me</a><br />\n去之前下載定尼泊爾離線地圖<br />\n最好搵日喺香港行山試下用 熟習下個app<br />\n<br />\n順便試下用一對行山杖減少雙腳負荷<br />\n可以上youtube睇教學 行山杖正確使用方法<br />\n尼泊爾租行山杖好平 講價就幾蚊港紙一日<br />\n<br />\nbackpack預備感冒退燒沖劑+桐灰暖包<br />\n山上夜晚會好瞓d"},{"pid":"9bb9292fb34b86f538c586a5c6abf5149bf90277","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:15:22.000Z","msg":"加德滿都搞落地簽證唔駛10分鐘<br />\n不過d關員有機會唔認得香港<br />\n印象中好似連form都唔駛填<br />\n<br />\n加德滿都 特里布萬國際機場<br />\n除左有國際航線<br />\n仲有內航機來回Pokhara<br />\n一程$500港紙 20分鐘到達<br />\n我係去淘寶book pokhara機票<br />\n平過當地旅行社agent<br />\n<br />\n登山證去acap office整 包影相即取<br />\n成個過程半個鐘 <br />\n收費幾貴下 acpc證+tim證<br />\npokhara既acap office就係pokhara機場隔離<br />\n行過去5分鐘 最好到埗即整<br />\nacap office亦即係tourist information centre<br />\n拎免費行山地圖"},{"pid":"d43c0d6a022d66478f63a6dba34b562513d3bfd0","tid":1816491,"uid":47470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af6530365a8f190d1074b20f65f3114337a041a3","tid":1816491,"uid":152584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"314f01f7d82a7ca2eea3b03fcad35df93bbc6ea7","tid":1816491,"uid":47470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T13:10:11.000Z","msg":"佢個所謂落地簽我分唔到同免簽有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中午時段到埗半個鐘出到去<br />\n9日夠行poon hill，我每日7/8點行到4點，慢慢行，第9日完<br />\n有長期行山經驗既我諗7日都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T17:37:19.000Z","msg":"沿途有餐廳? 同埋喺咪要請人幫手咩野 一個人大約洗幾錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:46:34.000Z","msg":"大把<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有山村就有餐廳，但價錢貴過城市就梗架啦<br />\n但對香港人黎講都唔會係貴<br />\n我個陣第一次行山，請人幫手一定要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />始終冇經驗冇體能，沿路見到既人都有7-8成有請<br />\n我諗就算你平時有行開香港山，呢d高海拔+長期行既行動都係穩陣d好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾錢唔記得，我17年去，好似係幾千港紙"},{"pid":"a78f5b67c45eac1bb0b581e9ece2d66d81e9db2b","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:12:27.000Z","msg":"尼泊爾幣去街邊找換店兌<br />\n機場 酒店 旅館都貴<br />\nphewa lake 搭的士去機場 300尼泊爾幣<br />\npokhara 搭的士去 naya pul 2000尼泊爾幣<br />\nphewa lake 係旅客聚居點 旅館餐廳商舖林立<br />\n<br />\n山上既tea house山屋+水源+3餐<br />\n2000尼泊爾幣一日<br />\n所有山上宿費/食物價格由尼泊爾政府規定<br />\n應該冇黑店"},{"pid":"6f31befd4a1755ba9e073b79e067fc4497be0889","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:39:31.000Z","msg":"其實3日可以行完abc<br />\n如果你唔繞上poon hill<br />\n因為Chhomrong上年通左車路<br />\n搭jeep已經上到Chhomrong<br />\n路程短左好多"},{"pid":"d9b7d2c2dd01228c11a03c5c3e92a152426ffc4a","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"abc + poon hill<br />\n每行2個鐘就有山屋畀你用膳住宿<br />\n基本上 水都可以唔駛帶<br />\n帶幾條snickers補充能量 pokhara買<br />\n<br />\n山上有雨通常下午時間<br />\n朝早5點起身 日行8個鐘<br />\n可以避開淋雨機會<br />\n<br />\n普通行山鞋行雪地太跣<br />\n鞋底要有深坑/Salomon/hoka<br />\n行山杖<br />\n山泥地直接用尖鐵頭/雪地用就戴上雪碟"},{"pid":"19e963ae2fd4b5c8e631fe7ddf2e28c2110d26d5","tid":1816491,"uid":205927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bad06e6769daa74c79bd2415b8d25ffb9d8a9ceb","tid":1816491,"uid":296005,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"224c9821de6f939ae7ef8ed12482e211495ead86","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T09:29:14.000Z","msg":"小弟打算4月頭同個fd去行abc<br />\n行程大約10日(連埋飛)<br />\n實質可能行8-9日左右<br />\n想問有冇可能行埋poon hill?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nOr淨係行abc算？好似唔洗咁趕<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs:2個都有做下運動既 嚟緊都準備train下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋想問下如果去到當地先搞簽證會唔會搞好耐?<br />\n麻煩曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"落地簽證，要等半曰<br />\n因為佢要揸車去整<br />\n<br />\n我上次都係around 4月去<br />\npoon hill 係值得去，abc 連poon hill 7 day係夠既<br />\n5 day 的話，你要行得幾快<br />\n<br />\nBTW日落後唔好沖涼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T17:08:38.000Z","msg":"上年去半個鐘唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd47c0f5c8a9d5783a1ab75315be35182b42e19","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9b7d2c2dd01228c11a03c5c3e92a152426ffc4a","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T02:17:59.000Z","msg":"abc + poon hill<br />\n每行2個鐘就有山屋畀你用膳住宿<br />\n基本上 水都可以唔駛帶<br />\n帶幾條snickers補充能量 pokhara買<br />\n<br />\n山上有雨通常下午時間<br />\n朝早5點起身 日行8個鐘<br />\n可以避開淋雨機會<br />\n<br />\n普通行山鞋行雪地太跣<br />\n鞋底要有深坑/Salomon/hoka<br />\n行山杖<br />\n山泥地直接用尖鐵頭/雪地用就戴上雪碟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T02:41:49.000Z","msg":"多謝師兄你咁詳細既分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a67f5ccd7e1cf2edf173b5743a3a66f44da12e","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"415241bb0c95fef0585a9b5684dda3e6b9a6f072","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T21:18:39.000Z","msg":"我果陣時自己一個行abc+poon hill<br />\n冇guide冇porter<br />\n由naya pul開始行<br />\npoon hill<br />\nannapurna base camp<br />\n順時針一圈回到naya pul<br />\n<br />\n我覺得唔易行 雖然d人話係家樂徑<br />\n3月尾開始有雨，但3000米以上有雪<br />\n高山反應同山上感冒好大件事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:02:11.000Z","msg":"想問總共行左幾多日<br />\n同埋唔請porter個背囊唔會好重咩<br />\n我仲考慮緊請唔請porter好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc8e558a1e188bcac1631859d7aa0af10166ac8e","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90a67f5ccd7e1cf2edf173b5743a3a66f44da12e","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0