orter 同guide 大概要幾錢？同埋係邊到有得請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T01:19:10.000Z","msg":"一google d資訊多到你睇唔曬<br />\n上背包客棧睇下人地推介啦"},{"pid":"481f62de9ffa6bbc6e5479e1d6cd6d2510502023","tid":1816491,"uid":8877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"我三年前去，poonhill + abc，淨係行都total 8日<br />\n<br />\n你10日好似會太趕，因為加德滿都去pokhara搭車都要6、7個鐘，如果搭飛機就1個鐘。同埋尼泊爾好似免簽證？我記得我當年去唔使簽。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得兩條路線都值得去，如果只係abc，行得快5日都ok<br />\n<br />\n我地當時4個人，兩男兩女，係香港一個月行一次山度（而家諗起都覺得好癲），所以請咗一個guide同兩個porter哥哥，四個人total 2000美金，8日內包食、住、登山證etc，但唔包食飯嘅飲品。<br />\n<br />\n另外，沖熱水涼要另外比錢，起初1蚊美金一個人，我記得去到最高要3蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但因為我好鍾意乾爽，所以日日都比錢沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地個guide好chur，每日6半叫醒我地，7點已經食完早餐要出發，行到大約4點度先休息，日日係度話要push我地嘅limit。所以我地4點到達guesthouse，9fing吓輪流沖涼、洗衫，然後食飯，再抖一陣，8點已經攰到即刻瞓著。<br />\n<br />\n有一日全日落雨都要行，底褲都濕晒，如果女仔黎m都唔知點搞，但我地行得好開心。有時行得快，3點到guesthouse冇咁chur就會同guide、porter哥哥玩啤牌，我地仲教識咗佢哋「kum棉胎」，大家圍住暖爐玩得好開心）<br />\n<br />\n我唔知4月算唔算旺季，我當年係10月去，都旺季，未必一定有住宿，如果冇事先安排，有可能要chur去下一個stop（都未必有），或者要行返去上一個stop，如果有guide佢就會預先打電話同同鄉安排好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我地個guide好好，係加德滿都酒店pick up我地，同我地一齊搭飛機去pokhara，之後陪我地搭巴士返加德滿都。因為同guide、porter相處得好好，最後每人比咗50美金tips（唔知算唔算多，當時仲係讀緊u，但見porter幫我地咩書包好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n題外話，見到中國遊客使人唔使本，要porter咩gip上山，屌，仲要行到半路話漏咗嘢係gip要開gip，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a575e217578d453767115d1409c7811d6f9f2d9","tid":1816491,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"尋日雪崩<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3044188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3044188&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=1bafdbde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3044188&h=a7c2c4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3044188</a>"},{"pid":"9cbb2110f2984aff11a8539f66f9993278a89e6a","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"481f62de9ffa6bbc6e5479e1d6cd6d2510502023","tid":1816491,"uid":8877,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T18:17:22.000Z","msg":"我三年前去，poonhill + abc，淨係行都total 8日<br />\n<br />\n你10日好似會太趕，因為加德滿都去pokhara搭車都要6、7個鐘，如果搭飛機就1個鐘。同埋尼泊爾好似免簽證？我記得我當年去唔使簽。<br />\n<br />\n我覺得兩條路線都值得去，如果只係abc，行得快5日都ok<br />\n<br />\n我地當時4個人，兩男兩女，係香港一個月行一次山度（而家諗起都覺得好癲），所以請咗一個guide同兩個porter哥哥，四個人total 2000美金，8日內包食、住、登山證etc，但唔包食飯嘅飲品。<br />\n<br />\n另外，沖熱水涼要另外比錢，起初1蚊美金一個人，我記得去到最高要3蚊美金<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但因為我好鍾意乾爽，所以日日都比錢沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地個guide好chur，每日6半叫醒我地，7點已經食完早餐要出發，行到大約4點度先休息，日日係度話要push我地嘅limit。所以我地4點到達guesthouse，9fing吓輪流沖涼、洗衫，然後食飯，再抖一陣，8點已經攰到即刻瞓著。<br />\n<br />\n有一日全日落雨都要行，底褲都濕晒，如果女仔黎m都唔知點搞，但我地行得好開心。有時行得快，3點到guesthouse冇咁chur就會同guide、porter哥哥玩啤牌，我地仲教識咗佢哋「kum棉胎」，大家圍住暖爐玩得好開心）<br />\n<br />\n我唔知4月算唔算旺季，我當年係10月去，都旺季，未必一定有住宿，如果冇事先安排，有可能要chur去下一個stop（都未必有），或者要行返去上一個stop，如果有guide佢就會預先打電話同同鄉安排好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋我地個guide好好，係加德滿都酒店pick up我地，同我地一齊搭飛機去pokhara，之後陪我地搭巴士返加德滿都。因為同guide、porter相處得好好，最後每人比咗50美金tips（唔知算唔算多，當時仲係讀緊u，但見porter幫我地咩書包好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n題外話，見到中國遊客使人唔使本，要porter咩gip上山，屌，仲要行到半路話漏咗嘢係gip要開gip，仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:35:03.000Z","msg":"thx bro <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2faf090996115c2412a33bc4e42eef50135d0c5","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a575e217578d453767115d1409c7811d6f9f2d9","tid":1816491,"uid":45765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"尋日雪崩<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3044188\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3044188&d=dJWoD07mVvvIIonm04m6IilkmYPKinjppKJkD7WQ61o%3D&h=1bafdbde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3044188&h=a7c2c4d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3044188</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢d意外既野...唉<br />\n預左有心理準備"},{"pid":"1766857988c3d628a4c305b73f50f9924539bf00","tid":1816491,"uid":45765,"like":0,"disl