8</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:36:16.000Z","msg":"咁恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過呢d意外既野...唉<br />\n預左有心理準備"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:37:12.000Z","msg":"老實講 佢地唔好彩<br />\n路線安全的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T13:44:10.000Z","msg":"時也，命也<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac0049fd188172b7624e796d12c88bd5406b72cf","tid":1816491,"uid":110155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6f31befd4a1755ba9e073b79e067fc4497be0889","tid":1816491,"uid":157187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:39:31.000Z","msg":"其實3日可以行完abc<br />\n如果你唔繞上poon hill<br />\n因為Chhomrong上年通左車路<br />\n搭jeep已經上到Chhomrong<br />\n路程短左好多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T21:56:21.000Z","msg":"其實真係唔好亂咁講<br />\n<br />\n唔係話三日唔得，但體能一定要好好，而且有高反會好大件事"},{"pid":"ed4e3b5fe136d8c9d5e8906d5e66c955c37e0c4b","tid":1816491,"uid":110155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-19T22:01:41.000Z","msg":"一般標準行程poonhill and abc 九日<br />\n<br />\n快嘅同埋坐jeep可以少一至兩日<br />\n<br />\n如果只係abc標準七日左右，可以快一兩日視乎體能<br />\n<br />\n不過講真，高山適應同體應無關，你適應唔好，體能勁都快唔到<br />\n<br />\n利伸：工作關係去過abc五次"},{"pid":"db3eb6baaee38fdcb2d00cd08846294a66c3881c","tid":1816491,"uid":146580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T04:47:45.000Z","msg":"多謝各位巴絲打既分享同提點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已book機票 <br />\n小弟計埋飛實際行得7日 所以都係慢慢行abc算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2個人應該打算請番個Porter-guide <br />\n祝我地好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nPs 仲有d裝備未買 分分鐘貴過張機票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}